headline: Alphabet and Tesla Earnings, Powell Speech and More: What to Watch Next Week
summary: Earnings season rolls on next week with the first of the Magnificent Seven tech names to report, Tesla and Alphabet. New economic data will shed more light on how tariffs are affecting U.S. consumer and business spending.
